ActCriminal Code
SubjectOrder Amending the Order Declaring an Amnesty Period (2006)
PrecisOrder Amending the ORDER DECLARING AN AMNESTY PERIOD (2006), which extends the amnesty period protecting individuals from incurring criminal liability under the Criminal Code as a result of the illegal possession of unregistered non-restricted firearms, for two years (from May 17, 2011 to May 16, 2013).
